                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6305" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MSL-0085</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8658 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">疫情笼罩下的“探鱼”探险之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The epidemic &quot;melancholy cloud&quot;, &quot;fish&quot; the road to explore the sun</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杜军，杨倩颖，艾子曼提&#183;吐尔孙</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">深圳市甘棠明善餐饮有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新冠疫情；危机管理；探鱼；长远发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">New crown epidemic; Crisis management; The fish; For the long-term development</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">探鱼是一家经营烤鱼的餐饮企业，凭借独特的怀旧风格，打造“最文艺的烤鱼店”，使探鱼成为餐饮行业的一匹黑马，五年内全国门店就突破了200家，覆盖了70多个城市。本应该是在餐饮这片宽阔的大海里遨游，却不料遭遇了新冠疫情的突然打击，让其猝不及防。本案例描述了探鱼在2020年新冠疫情中积极自救，寻找破局之法的过程，在这过程中探索出：及时从线下转到线上，积极拓展外卖市场；针对疫情研发了健康套餐；与盒马生鲜共享员工；涉足零售业等措施。探鱼不断地思考如何在危机中创造机会，也未雨绸缪地时刻准备应对挑战。本案例旨在引导学生深度思考新冠疫情下餐饮企业会遇到的危机，企业如何进行危机管理，从而实现企业的长远发展的目标。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Tanyu is a grilled fish catering enterprise. With its unique nostalgic style, it creates &quot;the most artistic grilled fish restaurant&quot;, making tanyu a dark horse in the catering industry. in five years, it had more than 200 stores nationwide, covering more than 70 cities. It should have been swimming in the wide sea of food and beverage, but it was suddenly hit by the COVID-19 pandemic, leaving him at his last gasp. This case describes the process of Tanyu actively saving themselves from the COVID-19 epidemic in 2020 and looking for ways to break the situation. In this process, it explores the following aspects: timely transfer from offline to online, and actively expand the takeout market; Health packages developed in response to the pandemic; Share staff with Hema Fresh; Steps such as getting into retail. Fish scouts are constantly thinking about how to create opportunities in a crisis, and are always prepared for the challenges ahead. This case aims to guide students to think deeply about the crisis that catering enterprises will encounter in the context of COVID-19, and how to carry out crisis management, so as to achieve the long-term development goals of enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《危机管理》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">4R危机管理理论；责任型领导理论；组织韧性相关理论；财务、风险管理相关知识</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-05</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
